{"tid":516151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港娛樂廢老代表］李克勤呢D恃老賣老既廢柒幾時先捨得死？","createTime":"2018-01-01T06:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:43:38.000Z","uid":49388,"like":40,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fef9167d509512f0e770f781f7949cbf2d7116af","tid":516151,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"唱歌毫無感情不得止，仲要唱腔老套一成不變悶到嘔<br />\n<br />\n唱足30年都未上到神台位就證明自己一早見哂底啦，但竟然仲不知廉恥地出新歌，仲要同D後生爭奬，真係完美演繹咩叫廢佬！<br />\n<br />\n失魂記又唔係好聽，中段<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追憶</span></span>由佢把口唱出簡直嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢D都係俾番學友eason唱把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全完美表達咩叫扮後生討好年青人又失敗既脫節廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢撚樣真係閪撚過姥姥楊千嬅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係，我認同老唔係問題，有實力就得。但廢老勤有幾多實力大家心知肚明，如果今日學友上台或玉置浩二黎香港拎最受歡迎歌星我就真係服啦，所以香港人自己都責任，點解你地仲未有人可以將李克勤呢D阻住地球轉既老柒頭踼走呢？<br />\n<br />\n結論李克勤都只係一件有D唱功但無用心唱歌呃足30飯食既地底泥。"},{"pid":"797e48a8bb7ad7fc065418df3c8f8f672eab5358","tid":516151,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"家下把聲又沙又西，憑乜仲呃飯食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係都俾hins上位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1798bb7014b57b70e39552ff2cfa1461ec4707a","tid":516151,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a226f10c5528e28a1d1736b1ef0225a235a30502","tid":516151,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eb61cda07d7d57b9908c8154c8e794572b4c8ea","tid":516151,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/